Introduction

BLACKSWAN is a four-member girl group under DR Music. They made their official debut on October 16, 2020 with their first full-length album Goodbye RANIA.

On May 26, 2022, new members Gabi and Sriya were revealed.

On July 31, 2022, DR Music officially announced that members Youngheun and Judy had graduated from the group.

On November 9, 2022, DR Music announced that Leia went on hiatus due to health concerns, it is assumed that she has silently departed from the group since.

On December 24, 2022, NVee was revealed as a new member in a Christmas pictorial behind-the-scene before being officially introduced on the 26th through an interview on the group's official channel.
